data.description: This beautiful Elk Grove home located in Sheldon North, offers both comfort and versatility. With beautiful Sunroom, Upgraded wood floors, vaulted ceilings, a convenient 1 bedroom and 1 bath on the first floors, 3 car garage for ample storage, a dual fireplace, it's a perfect blend of style and functionality. The flexible bedroom layout allows for a 5th bedroom or a home office, and the location provides easy access to schools, parks, and more.
